4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity specialists, requiring no prior knowledge. The program spans 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, with small class sizes of up to 16 participants. Students will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside mastering cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The curriculum also covers data loss prevention strategies and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. Instruction is available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop